replies.body:
One time, there was a sky bridge over my defense back in MCZone.... on Zalidor...

So i was busy managing my defense with a few others. I was giving out orders and such...

I looked up and spotted a skybridge. 

It was high up, very high.

So a diamond guy yelled "Im gonna use my no fall hacks." So he jumped down. 

I aimed my sights at WHERE he was falling to in the middle of the air and i managed to hit him in the chest. I knocked him off course and he fell into the void.

"Zintenka Hax!" He replied. 

I chuckled and reported him but he wasn't banned. I forgot his name... but i remember that that was one of my greatest kills ever :D
